cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.DC, cs.SI 

The paper discusses a machine learning algorithm for a network of multiple agents to collectively learn a series of tasks. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The use of multiple agents also suggests a focus on multi-agent systems, which is covered by cs.MA. The algorithm is designed to share knowledge in a distributed and decentralized manner, which suggests a focus on distributed computing, covered by cs.DC. Finally, the paper discusses empirical results on a variety of data sets, which suggests a focus on data science and statistical learning, covered by cs.SI.
